---
import SectionHeader from '@/components/section-header.astro';
---
<section class="al-section section" id="about">
  <SectionHeader num="01" title="About" subtitle="A short transmission" accent="amber" />
  <div class="al-about-body body">
    <p class="al-about-lead lead">
      Twenty years of building for the web, driven by the same curiosity I had on day one. I&rsquo;m
      Italian, from Florence. I like working the way I like being worked with:
      <span class="hl">approachable, plain-spoken, low ego</span>, and lightly sarcastic when the stack
      pretends to be the smartest person in the room.
    </p>
    <div class="al-about-secondary secondary">
      <p class="al-about-body2 body2">
        I care about <span class="hl">art in every form I can reach</span>: physical work and software,
        same rigor on structure and intent. In teams I stay <span class="hl">friendly and hands-on</span>
        by default: small meetings, pair when it helps, no mystique around who broke the build last week.
      </p>
      <p class="al-about-body2 body2">
        My focus is on governance and architectural standards: building the rails that strip away friction
        so teams can focus on shipping excellence. I remain in the code, balancing strategy with learning.
        <span class="hl">Pragmatism over hype</span>. If we over-engineered it, I&rsquo;ll say so kindly,
        then help you delete it. That counts as a good day.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="al-about-meta-row meta-row">
      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-k">Based</div>
        <div class="meta-v">Vienna, Austria</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-k">Mode</div>
        <div class="meta-v">Remote / Hybrid</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-k">Languages</div>
        <div class="meta-v">IT &middot; EN</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta">
        <div class="meta-k">Status</div>
        <div class="meta-v status">&#9679; In orbit &mdash; quietly building</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section {
    max-width: 1280px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 80px;
    position: relative;
  }
  .body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 24px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin: 0;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .hl {
    color: var(--gold-hi);
    font-weight: 500;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 60%, rgba(232,161,58,0.18) 60%);
    padding: 0 4px;
  }
  .body2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    margin: 0;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .secondary {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.35em;
  }
  .meta-row {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
    margin-top: 24px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .meta { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .meta-k {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-dim);
  }
  .meta-v {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--fg);
  }
  .status { color: var(--sage); }
</style>
